| Customer Deposit (Liability) | ‚Äî      | 10,000 |
--------------------------------------------------

üìå ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶Æ‡ßã‡¶ü Cash ‡¶ì ‡¶Æ‡ßã‡¶ü Deposit ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡ßü
‚ùå ‡¶ï‡ßã‡¶® ‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ï‚Äî‡¶§‡¶æ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡ßü ‡¶®‡¶æ

---

# üìä ‡ß©Ô∏è‚É£ Trial Balance ‡¶ï‡ßÄ?

## üîπ WHAT (‡¶ï‡¶ø)

Trial Balance ‡¶π‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶§‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ï‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá
üëâ ‡¶∏‡¶¨ GL ‡¶Ö‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶â‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶∞ Debit ‡¶ì Credit ‡¶Ø‡ßã‡¶ó‡¶´‡¶≤ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§

‡¶Æ‡ßÇ‡¶≤ ‡¶®‡¶ø‡ßü‡¶Æ:

> Total Debit = Total Credit

---

## üîπ WHY (‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶® ‡¶¶‡¶∞‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞)
        - ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨ ‡¶†‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ü‡¶õ‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶ø ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶á
        - GL Posting ‡¶∏‡¶†‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶ø ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∂‡ßç‡¶ö‡¶ø‡¶§
        - Financial Statement ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶Ü‡¶ó‡ßá ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï

---

## üîπ HOW (‡¶â‡¶¶‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶∞‡¶£)

### Trial Balance
----------------------------------------------
| Account          | Debit      | Credit     |
| ---------------- | ---------- | ---------- |
| Cash             | 10,000     | ‚Äî          |
| Customer Deposit | ‚Äî          | 10,000     |
----------------------------------------------
| Total            | 10,000     | 10,000 |
----------------------------------------------

‚úîÔ∏è ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶õ‡ßá ‚Üí ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨ ‡¶†‡¶ø‡¶ï
‚ùå ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶≤‡¶≤‡ßá ‚Üí Error / Posting issue

---

# üîç Ledger vs GL vs Trial Balance (Clear Comparison)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶∑‡ßü          | Ledger (Sub-Ledger)       | GL                  | Trial Balance  |
| ------------- | ------------------------- | ------------------- | -------------- |
| Level         | Detail (Customer-wise)    | Summary (Head-wise) | Summary Check  |
| Purpose       | Daily ops, SMS, Statement | Financial records   | Accuracy check |
| Customer Name | ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá                      | ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ             | ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ        |
| Output        | Balance per account       | Total per head      | Debit = Credit |
| CBS Role      | Operational               | Official book       | Validation     |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---

# üß† ‡¶Æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶∏‡¶π‡¶ú ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶®
        > Ledger = ‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶§‡¶æ
        > GL = ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶§‡¶æ
        > Trial Balance = ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨ ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã‡¶∞ ‡¶§‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ï‡¶æ

---

## üéØ Interview / Exam One-Liners
        - Ledger records detailed transactions for a specific account.
        - General Ledger summarizes all ledgers for reporting.
        - Trial Balance checks whether debits equal credits.

---



############################## 02. üßæ ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶á ‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶ú‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶∂‡¶®: Ledger ‚Üí GL ‚Üí Trial Balance (side-by-side)  ##########################

‡¶ö‡¶≤‡ßÅ‡¶® ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶á ‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶ú‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶∂‡¶® (Branch Cash Deposit) Ledger ‚Üí GL ‚Üí Trial Balance
üëâ side-by-side, ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶á ‡¶™‡ßá‡¶ú‡ßá, copy-study friendly‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶ø‡•§


## üéØ Scenario (‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶á ‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶ú‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶∂‡¶®)

üëâ ‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ï Savings Account-‡¶è ‡ßß‡ß¶,‡ß¶‡ß¶‡ß¶ ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶∂ ‡¶ú‡¶Æ‡¶æ ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶≤ (Branch Counter)

---

# üßæ ‚ë† Ledger (Sub-Ledger) ‚Äî Detail / Customer-wise

> ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ï‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶§‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶§‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶§ ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá (SMS/Statement ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶á)

### üßë Customer Deposit Sub-Ledger

-------------------------------------------------------------
| Date  | Particulars         | Debit | Credit |    Balance |
| ----- | ------------------- | ----: | -----: | ---------: |
| Today | Branch Cash Deposit |     ‚Äî | 10,000 | 10,000     |
-------------------------------------------------------------

### üè¶ Cash (Vault/Teller) Sub-Ledger

--------------------------------------------------------
| Date  | Particulars   |  Debit | Credit |     Balance |
| ----- | ------------- | -----: | -----: | ----------: |
| Today | Cash Received | 10,000 |      ‚Äî | +10,000 |
--------------------------------------------------------

Logic (Bank POV):

- Customer Deposit = Liability ‚Üë ‚Üí Credit
- Cash = Asset ‚Üë ‚Üí Debit

---

# üìò ‚ë° General Ledger (GL) ‚Äî Summary / Head-wise

> ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ï ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶Æ ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶á‚Äî‡¶∂‡ßÅ‡¶ß‡ßÅ ‡¶Æ‡ßã‡¶ü ‡¶Ö‡¶ô‡ßç‡¶ï
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| GL Code | GL Head                     |      Debit |     Credit |
| ------- | --------------------------- | ---------: | ---------: |
| 101     | Cash (Asset)                | 10,000      |          ‚Äî |
| 201     | Savings Deposit (Liability) |          ‚Äî  | 10,000     |
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Why GL?
- Financial Statement, Audit, Central Bank ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßã‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü‚Äî‡¶∏‡¶¨ ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá

---

# üìä ‚ë¢ Trial Balance ‚Äî Accuracy Check

> Rule: Total Debit = Total Credit
---------------------------------------------
| Account         |      Debit |     Credit |
| --------------- | ---------: | ---------: |
| Cash            |     10,000 |          ‚Äî |
| Savings Deposit |          ‚Äî |     10,000 |
---------------------------------------------
| Total       | 10,000 | 10,000 |

‚úîÔ∏è Balanced ‚Üí Transaction Complete

---

## üîç Side-by-Side Summary (‡¶è‡¶ï ‡¶®‡¶ú‡¶∞‡ßá)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Stage         | ‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡ßü         | Customer-wise? | ‡¶â‡¶¶‡ßç‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶∂‡ßç‡¶Ø              |
| ------------- | ---------------- | -------------- | --------------------|
| Ledger (SL)   | Detail entries   | ‚úÖ ‡¶π‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Å          | SMS, Statement, Ops |
| GL            | Head-wise totals | ‚ùå ‡¶®‡¶æ           | FS, Audit           |
| Trial Balance | Debit=Credit     | ‚ùå ‡¶®‡¶æ           | Accuracy check      |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

---

## üß† ‡¶Æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡ßß-‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶®‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶™
> Ledger ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ñ‡ßá ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶§‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶§ ‚Üí GL ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶æ‡ßü ‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶∏‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡ßá‡¶™ ‚Üí Trial Balance ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶≤‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∂‡ßç‡¶ö‡ßü‡¶§‡¶æ

---

## üéØ Exam / Interview One-Liner
> -‚ÄúA transaction first updates sub-ledgers for detail, then posts to the general ledger for totals, and finally passes the trial balance check.‚Äù-


######################################### 03. üëâ ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶ö‡ßá Balance Sheet ‡¶ï‡ßÄ‚Äî WHAT (‡¶ï‡¶ø), WHY (‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶®), HOW (‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá)? Balance Sheet ‡¶¨‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶Æ Trial Balance #########################################


---

## üìä Balance Sheet ‡¶ï‡ßÄ? (WHAT)

Balance Sheet ‡¶π‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶¨‡¶∞‡¶£‡ßÄ (Financial Statement),
‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∑‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶§‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶ñ‡ßá ‡¶ï‡ßã‡¶®‡ßã ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶∑‡ßç‡¶†‡¶æ‡¶® (‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï)‚Äî

* ‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶™‡¶¶ (Assets) ‡¶Ü‡¶õ‡ßá
* ‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶¶‡¶æ‡ßü (Liabilities) ‡¶Ü‡¶õ‡ßá
* ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ Equity ‡¶ï‡¶§

üëâ ‡¶∏‡¶¨ ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶•‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§

üìå ‡¶∏‡¶π‡¶ú ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶∑‡¶æ‡ßü:
> Balance Sheet = ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∑‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶õ‡¶¨‡¶ø (Snapshot)

---

## ‚ùì ‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶® Balance Sheet ‡¶¶‡¶∞‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞? (WHY)

1Ô∏è‚É£ ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø
2Ô∏è‚É£ ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶§‡¶ü‡¶æ ‡¶∂‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶∂‡¶æ‡¶≤‡ßÄ/‡¶ù‡ßÅ‡¶Å‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßÇ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶£ ‡¶¨‡ßã‡¶ù‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø
3Ô∏è‚É£ Central Bank ‡¶ì Audit ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßã‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶Ç‡ßü‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø
4Ô∏è‚É£ ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶®‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßã‡¶ó‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßÄ ‡¶ì ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶™‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶∏‡¶ø‡¶¶‡ßç‡¶ß‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßç‡¶§‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø
5Ô∏è‚É£ Accounting Equation ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶≤‡¶õ‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶ø ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶á ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá

---

## üßÆ Balance Sheet-‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡ßÇ‡¶≤ ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßÄ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶£ (HOW)

```
Assets = Liabilities + Equity
```

üëâ Balance Sheet ‡¶∏‡¶¨‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßü ‡¶è‡¶á ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßÄ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶£‡ßá ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßç‡¶∏ ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá‡•§

## üè¶ ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶Ç Balance Sheet-‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶ó‡¶†‡¶®

### üîµ Assets (‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ø‡¶æ ‡¶Ü‡¶õ‡ßá)
* Cash & Bank Balance
* Loans & Advances
* Investments
* Fixed Assets (Building, ATM)


### üî¥ Liabilities (‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶¶‡¶æ‡ßü)
* Customer Deposits (Savings, Current, FD)
* Borrowings
* Payables


### üü¢ Equity (‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ö‡¶Ç‡¶∂)
* Paid-up Capital
* Retained Earnings
* Reserve & Surplus


## üßæ Real Banking Example (‡¶∏‡¶π‡¶ú)

üëâ ‡¶ß‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶®, ‡¶Ü‡¶ú ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶•‡¶æ:

### Balance Sheet (As on Today)
--------------------------------------------------------------
| Assets    |     Amount | Liabilities & Equity |     Amount |
| --------- | ---------: | -------------------- | ---------: |
| Cash      |     10,000 | Customer Deposit     |     10,000 |
--------------------------------------------------------------
| Total     | 10,000     | Total                | 10,000     |
--------------------------------------------------------------

‚úîÔ∏è Balanced


## üîÅ Ledger ‚Üí GL ‚Üí Trial Balance ‚Üí Balance Sheet
        * Ledger: Detail ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨
        * GL: Head-wise ‡¶Æ‡ßã‡¶ü
        * Trial Balance: Debit = Credit ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï
        * Balance Sheet: ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∂


## üß† Balance Sheet ‡¶¨‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶Æ Trial Balance (Confusion Clear)

-------------------------------------------------------------
| ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶∑‡ßü     | Trial Balance  | Balance Sheet                 |
| -------- | -------------- | ----------------------------- |
| ‡¶â‡¶¶‡ßç‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶∂‡ßç‡¶Ø   | ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨ ‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã   | ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶•‡¶æ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã            |
| ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßü     | ‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßã‡¶®‡ßã ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßü     | ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶¶‡¶ø‡¶∑‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶§‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶ñ‡ßá                 |
| Account  | ‡¶∏‡¶¨ GL          | Asset, Liability, Equity     |
| Output   | Debit = Credit | Assets = Liabilities + Equity |
-------------------------------------------------------------

## üéØ Exam / Interview One-Liner
> Balance Sheet shows the financial position of a bank at a specific point in time.


## üß† ‡¶Æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶®
> Trial Balance ‡¶¨‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨ ‡¶†‡¶ø‡¶ï,
> Balance Sheet ‡¶¨‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶Ç‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶§‡¶ü‡¶æ ‡¶∂‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡•§






.
